Yeah, man, go for it! Did I see an F-14 in those pictures?

You did indeed. I actually have two 14's, one swept and on "unswept". I'm pretty happy with it, it came out well for the limited time I put into that aircraft. Some take less time than others, and some designs fight you the whole build. I'm new to the forum scene so bare with me while I try to file share. Let me know what everyone thinks of my aircraft, I have quite a few more that are not shown and If enough people like my builds I'll take requests.
